# 7. CRM Intake & Prioritization Framework

## Intake Requirements

All CRM enhancement requests must include:

* Business problem statement
* Requested enhancement
* Business owner
* Business justification
* User impact
* Revenue impact
* Compliance impact
* Requested timeline
* Systems impacted
* Supporting documentation

---

## Prioritization Model

| Criteria             | Weight |
| -------------------- | ------ |
| Revenue Impact       | 30%    |
| User Impact          | 25%    |
| Compliance Risk      | 20%    |
| Strategic Alignment  | 15%    |
| Technical Complexity | 10%    |

